lines.text: حق واسطا : پارت سرکار قانون و نياء
سركاري بولي پاگر لاء انبين انستیتیوت آف
سنة الأجي آدیپور (كي) چپائي پترو کیو.
On behalf of Ministry of Law & Justice, Legislative
Department, Official Language Wing, published by
This is the Sindhi translation of the Constitution of India. In
this edition the text of the Constitution has been brought up-to
date by incorporating therein all the amendments upto and
including the Constitution (Seventy Eighth Amendment) Act, 1995.
The work relating to translation of Amendments Nos. 46 to
78 and Sixth Schedule to the Constitution (Amendment) Act, 1995
and printing of Sindhi version of the Constitution was entrusted to
the Indian Institute of Sindhology, Adipur (Kutch). We are thankful
to Dr. Satish Rohra, Director of the Institute for timely production
SECRETARY TO THE GOVT. OF INDIA
